CaumeDSE Web Client
===================

HTML5 single-page application with a Python CORS proxy.  The browser UI
covers the same set of operations as the CLI clients: encrypted secret
storage, encrypted CSV databases, user/org info, and the audit log.


CONTENTS
========
I.    How it works
II.   Prerequisites
III.  Starting the proxy
